OL,3,CThe last of the neon sign makers
OL,4,Cfighting to save the craft
OL,6,F"If it's not made with glass and
OL,7,Ffilled with gas, it's not neon. The
OL,8,FLED versions are cheap to manufacture
OL,9,Fand easier to get hold of - and it's a
OL,10,Fmass produced product, we just can't
OL,11,Fcompete with those prices."
OL,13,FAt Neon Creations, Catherine says the
OL,14,Ffalse comparisons are costing them
OL,15,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
