OL,3,CThe last of the neon sign makers
OL,4,Cfighting to save the craft
OL,6,F"These alternatives are half the price
OL,7,For less - so if a customer has a quote
OL,8,Ffor neon and an LED product they are
OL,9,Fbeing told is neon, it causes some
OL,10,Fconfusion about why ours are so much
OL,11,Fmore expensive, and they go for the
OL,12,Fmuch cheaper option".
OL,14,FThe company has also come under
OL,15,Fcriticism from customers who buy
OL,16,Fcheaper LED alternatives online, and
OL,17,Fthen ask traditional crafters like
OL,18,Fthose at Neon Creations why they can't
OL,19,Frepair them when they break.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
