OL,3,CThe last of the neon sign makers
OL,4,Cfighting to save the craft
OL,6,FA Greater Manchester MP is now adding
OL,7,Fher voice to a campaign calling on the
OL,8,FGovernment to protect the neon
OL,9,Findustry, either though a
OL,10,Fcertification mark that can only be
OL,11,Fapplied to genuine neon products, or a
OL,12,Fdefined British standard which gives
OL,13,Fthe term legal protection.
OL,15,FYasmin Qureshi, who represents Bolton
OL,16,FSouth and Walkden, says this will
OL,17,Fimprove transparency for customers and
OL,18,Flet them know when they are buying
OL,19,F"the real deal".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
