OL,3,CThe last of the neon sign makers
OL,4,Cfighting to save the craft
OL,6,F"It should not be acceptable for
OL,7,Fretailers, large or small, to market a
OL,8,Fproduct as neon when it contains no
OL,9,Fglass, no gas and no craftsmanship.
OL,11,F"We have rightly challenged fake olive
OL,12,Foils and falsely labelled meat; we
OL,13,Fmust apply the same standard in this
OL,14,Fcase."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
