OL,3,CThe last of the neon sign makers
OL,4,Cfighting to save the craft
OL,6,F"Let us not forget the cultural value
OL,7,Fof neon. It is signage, but it is also
OL,8,Fart; it evokes memories of cinemas,
OL,9,Fdiners, music venues and city
OL,10,Fskylines. It is a symbol of expression
OL,11,Fand identity, and to lose it would be
OL,12,Fto dim the vibrant glow of Britain's
OL,13,Fcreative past."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
