OL,3,CThe last of the neon sign makers
OL,4,Cfighting to save the craft
OL,6,F"I encourage neon crafters to make a
OL,7,Fsubmission to the inventories of
OL,8,Fliving heritage in the UK when we open
OL,9,Fthe call for submissions later this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,F"That is a fantastic opportunity for
OL,13,Fthe neon craft community to advocate
OL,14,Ffor their craft, raise awareness and
OL,15,Fbe part of a wider conversation on
OL,16,Fliving heritage."
